## User Files

Canonical paths are **lowercase**; see [canonical-paths.md](docs/canonical-paths.md).

```
users/[user-id]/
├── self.md                  # Who they ARE (identity + three-dimension mind)
├── self-skills.md           # What they CAN DO (capability index; legacy skills.md still resolved)
├── self-archive.md          # EVIDENCE — raw activities + § VIII gated approved log
├── self-evidence.md         # optional compatibility pointer
├── session-log.md           # Interaction history
├── recursion-gate.md        # Pipeline staging (candidates + processed)
└── artifacts/               # Raw files (writing samples, artwork)
```

## Bot Files

```
bot/
├── core.py           # Shared emulation logic (Telegram + WeChat)
├── bot.py            # Telegram bot
├── wechat_bot.py     # WeChat Official Account bot
├── prompt.py         # All LLM prompts (SYSTEM, ANALYST, LOOKUP, REPHRASE)
└── requirements.txt  # Python dependencies
```

